FeedPackage.Description:
ThymeTech DLL
All Classes below are thread safe
- Windows Validation (confirm that windows is legal and registered) - Versioning of EXE's and DLL's - Twitter intergration (send / read messages) - Thread Management (make controls - RichTextBox, TextBox, ProgressBar) thread safe - Control over system date and time (ability to update / change / read the time and date) - Convert Datatable -> CSV file (specify 3 parameters [DataTable, Separator for CSV eg: ",", and outputFileName) - Convert CSV -> Datatable - similar to above - Convert Dictionary -> CSV - Convert CSV -> Dictionary - Registration (GUI to register, Class to verify registration) - Database utilities (MySQL, Pervasive, MsSQL) - like transaction handling (being, commit, rollback), connecting, etc... - Logging class - link class to RichTextBox on form, all logging will go to richtextbox and be saved in log file with date stamp - FTP Utilities - isValidConnection, Connect, GetFileList, DownloadFileAsText, DeleteFile, UploadFile - Encryption Class (encrypt/decrypt our own registration and passwords, and Pastel Evolution passwords) - Emailing class - Validate Address, SendGmail, SendEmail - Configuration File (we use this to save settings etc.., its a standard windows ini file) - Class that stores our common images / logos as byte array's and returns an object of type "Image" - Zip / Unzip all files types (7zip, Rar, Zip, Gz, etc...) - view progress of unzip/zip also possible - Website API's - City Power - Eskom - Eye Witness News - Google Maps - Internet Explorer class - controls IE, allows you to open a IE window and send key's to items on the HTML based on their name / id and press buttons - Microsoft Excel class - export datatable to excel, read excel sheet as datatable - CSV File reading / writing - and handling advanced things like commas wrapped in double-quotes etc..
